Ubuntu 16

1. Add the masternode user

adduser masternode && adduser masternode sudo


2. Install as masternode user

a) change to the masternode user
sudo masternode

b) verify you have done so
whoami

c) change to your home directory
cd


3. Run the Sparks insallation script

a) download the script
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/stooky/mn/master/Sparks/sparks-install.sh

b) make the script executable
chmod +x sparks-install.sh

c) run the script
./sparks-install.sh



